_:Nf74d0d4daaae48978cd62e0766bac476 <http://schema.org/description> "The Fair Work Agency (FWA) is responsible for enforcing workers’ rights. We’re a single point of contact for workers who believe their rights have not been upheld. FWA is an executive agency, sponsored by the Department for Business and Trade ." .
